OL,5, The cost of housing migrants in hotels 
OL,6, has risen to #8m a day, according to   
OL,7, new figures from the Home Office.      
OL,9,FThe use of hotels has increased over   
OL,10,Fthe last few years as the number of    
OL,11,Fpeople entering the UK illegally or    
OL,12,Fclaiming asylum has hit record levels. 
OL,14,FThe government has promised to "reduce"
OL,15,Fthe use of hotels to house migrants    
OL,16,Fwhile their claims are processed.      
OL,18,FIn March the BBC learned around 400    
OL,19,Fhotels were being used, costing nearly 
OL,20,F#7m a day.                             
